	* awk.h (DEREF): Add an assert.
	* builtin.c (do_typeof): Add comments, cases where not to deref.
	* debug.c (print_instruction): Add Op_push_arg_untyped.
	* interpret.h (r_interpret): Additional comments / tweaks for
	Op_push_arg_untyped.

